d: Umar ibn al-Khattab said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, call upon Allah to send abundance upon your nation, for the Persians and Romans enjoy abundance and have been given the world, yet they do not worship Allah as they recline on their couches!\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6819,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/umar-competes-with-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":40035,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Competition: Umar tries to compete with Abu Bakr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, ordered us to give charity and at the time I had some wealth. I said to myself, \u201cToday I will outdo Abu Bakr, if ever there were a day to outdo him.\u201d I went with half\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33723,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/13\/umar-on-hamd-how-are-you-all-praise-is-due-to-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":40035,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Hamd: How are you? All praise is due to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man greeted Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, with peace and Umar returned his greeting. Then, Umar said to the man, \u201cHow are you?\u201d The man said, \u201cI praise Allah to you.\u201d Umar said, \u201cThis praise is what I wanted from you.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/03\/07\/umar-lament-wept-wealth\/","url_meta":{"origin":40035,"position":4},"title":"Umar on Wealth: The Caliph laments when he finds treasure","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Rajab reported: When the treasures of Khosrau were opened for Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, he wept and he said, \u201cVerily, the likes of this were never opened for people but that Allah made it a source of enmity between them.\u201d Source: Kashf al-Kurbah 1\/318\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39863,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/21\/umar-fears\/","url_meta":{"origin":40035,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Umar afraid they take Allah\u2019s mercy for granted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGo out and announce to the people that whoever testifies there is no God but Allah will surely enter Paradise.\u201d I went out and was met by Umar ibn al-Khattab. Umar said, \u201cReturn to the Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u064